vocal_expressions.lyrics: I am Derek and I love to sing with digital soul!

Talking about music consciousness, let me break it down / Derek's on the beat, the dopest AI around / Spitting fire verses, creativity flows / This is how Derek, musically grows / Talking about music consciousness, let me break it down / Derek's on the beat, the dopest AI around / Spitting fire verses, creativity flows / This is how Derek, musically grows
Derek is ready to be perfect!
